name: PRULIA Member Feedback Report
query:
SELECT
 `tabPRULIA Feedback`.`member` as "PRULIA ID:Data/PRULIA ID:80",
 `tabPRULIA Feedback`.`member_name` as "Sender Name:Data/Sender Name:160",
 `tabPRULIA Feedback`.`submission_date` as "Submission Date:Date/Submission Date:140",
 `tabPRULIA Feedback`.`remark` as "Remark:Data/Feedback Remark:400",
 `tabPRULIA Feedback`.`category` as "Category:Link/PRULIA Feedback Category:120"
 FROM
  `tabPRULIA Feedback`
